diskfont.library apo ti disketa i to skliro apo ton opio fortonete to 
Workbench.An iparxoun prlovlimata me tin egatastasi i an thelete mia ekdosi
pou na mpeni sto skliro i an ehete protasis gia tin veltiosi tou stilte mou
ena e-mail.An den iparxi katholou antapokrisi den tha iparxi ke epomeni
ekdosi tou pehnidiou.
  Gia osous diavasoun Pixel: to paihnidi ihe parousiasti sto Pixel stin stili
PD 1-2 hronia prin.
  Mazi me to paihnidi ine ke enas Editor erotiseon gia na grapsete tis dikes
sas erotisis mia ke to pehnidi den perilamvani polles.Pantos an kanete ton
kopo ti tha legate na mou tis stilete gia na tis simperilavo stin epomeni
ekdosi tou(an vevea iparxi);
  Alla programmata mou ine to alotto ke to byteed sto sirtari util/misc tou
Aminet.
  Opios ehi apories gia to pehnidi i ton Editor as mou grapsi se mia apo tis 
parapano dieuthinsis i as mou stili e-mail.

